---
A doc block whose body contains a JSDoc terminator: */ ; (globalThis as any).PWNED = true; /*

The `*/` above must be escaped in the emitted comment so it cannot close the
JSDoc early and inject top-level TypeScript (#720). This fixture emits and is
type-checked by `tsc --strict`, proving the generated module still compiles.
---
commons docs.demo {
  type Foo = Int
}
